videos.description: With three defenders on her, Jessica Shepard collects a rebound, eventually getting the ball to Brianna Turner for a layup.
videos.headline: Turner hits layup after good defense

videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale puts Notre Dame up 53-46 in the third with a deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Ogunbowale sinks deep 3
